### Welcome to the M-A Chronicle's GitHub Page
The M-A Chronicle is the official newspaper for Melon-Atherton High School. As we are working hard to provide the best content we are working on some high-tech code and projects here. for more information go to our [site](http://www.machronicle.com/)>


### Support or Contact
For further information check http://www.machronicle.com/
